  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/847680/extras/5cd3e90266a372bd55878acf4422b3c0.avif?t=1618408938\" width=603 height=151 /></span><br><br>In this Gothic story of deep bonds and chilling mystery, <strong>a young girl named Esther </strong>ventures deep within a forgotten forest.<br><br>There, she seeks out a potential cure for her mysterious illness: a life-leeching plague known as <strong><i>the Pale Cachexia.</i></strong><br><br>But when Esther meets <strong>Seina,</strong> who lives all alone in a towering manor, the two girls are drawn to each other in a tale of friendship, sorrow, and bitter loneliness.<br><br>Their story is shadowed by the dark secrets of the manor and its <strong>graveyard,</strong> which haunts Esther even in her deepest dreams.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/847680/extras/36d669a028dd2c3cc939fdf2cc801b9c.avif?t=1618408938\" width=603 height=151 /></span><br><br><strong>Genres:</strong> Kinetic novel, Gothic fantasy, drama, horror<br><strong>Rating:</strong> PG-13 (language/mild horror)<br><strong>Story Type:</strong> Linear/kinetic<br><strong>Length:</strong> 48,000 words (4-5 hours playtime)<br><br><strong>Accessibility Features:</strong> Sound/Music closed captions, OpenDyslexic font option, disable bright flashes option<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/847680/extras/289308e3ed4cdad64b7c1dde2cc40a45.avif?t=1618408938\" width=603 height=151 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/847680/extras/a27800225ada83e707635ada769f100b.avif?t=1618408938\" width=602 height=546 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"ht